{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as I know, it was 1860, and she died in 1935-- and in Krakow, of course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was-- she lived with us and she was-- when she married, Fabian Barber, my grandfather, he was about 65, and she was 18.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was his youngest daughter-- he sent for a wife, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was friend of his youngest daughter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- but he was this one who was such a fighter for, well, Polish independence, and he also was a quite well-to-do gentleman.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he built that house for Grandma, and in this house was my mother born, and I was born, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the house was taken away from us, first by the Germans, then by the communists.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Until now, I cannot even get our house back in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But Grandma was living with us, and we were living in-- you see, every tenant in this house, it was living from generation to generation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were all friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I came to visit, visit to see what is going on about 15 years ago or so, there was no one of the old tenants there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They even hardly allowed me to go, and we had the whole second floor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And to take a look at my place where I was born.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, Grandma had five children, and the oldest was the uncle, engineer, Uncle Ignacy, who was also in Krakow and had two children, two boys, my cousins.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then he was much older than my mother, and he perished in ghetto Krakow during that October transport, probably, I don't know where, to Sobibor or to else, and together with his youngest son.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1942. 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rosaelia, R-O-S-A-E-L-I-A Barber, B-A-R-B-E-R.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that uncle was Ignacy, I-G-N-A-C-Y.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
